==English==
===Etymology 1===
A nickname for various LDVs made by the Datsun motor company. It is not a brand name.

====Noun====
{{en-noun}}
#(South African) A generic name for any light delivery vehicle.

===Etymology 2===
Afrikaans: ''bak'': bowl, dish.

====Noun====
{{en-noun}}
#(South African) A covered bowl, similar to a [[Tupperware]] container.
